				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I tried to use the following macro last night and it wouldnt work:
<br />

<br />
/pause 2, /target &lt;Your Name&gt; 
<br />
/pause 10, /cast &lt;Spell Slot Number&gt; 
<br />
/pause 2, /pet target 
<br />
/pause 10, /cast &lt;Spell Slot Number&gt; 
<br />
/assist 
<br />

<br />
I kept getting "you haven't recovered messages"
<br />

<br />
so I had to do something like this:
<br />

<br />
/pause 2, /target Bithnar 
<br />
