				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I had the same problem Bithnar but i found i could get by with 35 instead of 45 pause but sometimes I wouldn't get targeted so increased the first pause to 5 like this:
<br />

<br />
/pause 5, /target Ozze
<br />
/pause 35, /cast 6
<br />
/pause 10, /pet target
<br />
/pause 10, /cast 6
<br />
/assist
<br />

<br />
The problem with this macro now that it works is, it takes way too long and I miss many swings using it and the benefit doesn't last long at all.
<br />

<br />
I'm going back to just pulling with drowsy and nuking with ice spear, will wait till 39 when i get dex buff and/or try to find some nice equipment with dex so i can raise my skills faster.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
